Resonance7 first-run marker.

This file is tracked in Git. A fresh clone includes it so agents know bootstrap has not run yet.

After you run:
  python library/tools/scripts/setup_workspace.py

the script removes this file locally. That is expected. Do not commit the deletion to Git
(the marker should stay in the upstream repo for the next clone).

If you see this file, runtime directories under library/sessions/, projects/, tests/, etc.
may be missing. Run setup_workspace.py before session logging or project pairing work.
